{"snp5.4:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.4 ","snp5.4:0.2":"Punnakamanavapuccha ","snp5.4:1.1":"“Anejam muladassavim, ","snp5.4:1.2":"(iccayasma punnako) ","snp5.4:1.3":"Atthi panhena agamam; ","snp5.4:1.4":"Kim nissita isayo manuja, ","snp5.4:1.5":"Khattiya brahmana devatanam; ","snp5.4:1.6":"Yannamakappayimsu puthudha loke, ","snp5.4:1.7":"Pucchami tam bhagava bruhi me tam”. ","snp5.4:2.1":"“Ye kecime isayo manuja, ","snp5.4:2.2":"(punnakati bhagava) ","snp5.4:2.3":"Khattiya brahmana devatanam; ","snp5.4:2.4":"Yannamakappayimsu puthudha loke, ","snp5.4:2.5":"Asisamana punnaka itthattam; ","snp5.4:2.6":"Jaram sita yannamakappayimsu”. ","snp5.4:3.1":"“Ye kecime isayo manuja, ","snp5.4:3.2":"(iccayasma punnako) ","snp5.4:3.3":"Khattiya brahmana devatanam; ","snp5.4:3.4":"Yannamakappayimsu puthudha loke, ","snp5.4:3.5":"Kaccissu te bhagava yannapathe appamatta; ","snp5.4:3.6":"Atarum jatinca jaranca marisa, ","snp5.4:3.7":"Pucchami tam bhagava bruhi me tam”. ","snp5.4:4.1":"“Asisanti thomayanti abhijappanti juhanti, ","snp5.4:4.2":"(punnakati bhagava) ","snp5.4:4.3":"Kamabhijappanti paticca labham; ","snp5.4:4.4":"Te yajayoga bhavaragaratta, ","snp5.4:4.5":"Natarimsu jatijaranti brumi”. ","snp5.4:5.1":"“Te ce natarimsu yajayoga, ","snp5.4:5.2":"(iccayasma punnako) ","snp5.4:5.3":"Yannehi jatinca jaranca marisa; ","snp5.4:5.4":"Atha ko carahi devamanussaloke, ","snp5.4:5.5":"Atari jatinca jaranca marisa; ","snp5.4:5.6":"Pucchami tam bhagava bruhi me tam”. ","snp5.4:6.1":"“Sankhaya lokasmi paroparani, ","snp5.4:6.2":"(punnakati bhagava) ","snp5.4:6.3":"Yassinjitam natthi kuhinci loke; ","snp5.4:6.4":"Santo vidhumo anigho niraso, ","snp5.4:6.5":"Atari so jatijaranti brumi”ti. ","snp5.4:6.6":"Punnakamanavapuccha tatiya. "}